node.text:
I am excited to be partnering with @bedheadbytigi to celebrate Pride month this year! 🌈 #AD
 
Styling our hair is a beautiful and fun way to express ourselves especially during pride month!! Bed Head's styling products are all about creativity and self-expression for everyone!
 
To celebrate their love for the LGBTQIA+ community, @haircraigmarsden and I have created a gorgeous Pride look, making the most of my silver streak with sparkling tinsel strands to turn heads at Pride events this summer. I’ve even got my own personalised bottle of Queen for a Day, and my UK followers can make their own at yourbedhead.com. Use promo code QUEENVISAGE for 25% off for limited time.
 
Check out the full range at bedhead.com
Be You. Be Bold. Be Bed Head.
 
#BeYouBeBoldBeBeadHead
#LetYourCreativityRule
#BedHeadbyTIGI
 
Products used:
Queen for a Day thickening spray
After Party smoothing cream
Masterpiece shiny hairspray

node.text: Here we display South Plainfield's answer to Meryl Streep. This was an audition for a scholarship to an ARTS program to help me pay for college. This is my real accent before intense training at AMDA to lose it. How I haven't been cast in every film and TV project is BEYOND ME. I was forced to do a "classical" piece only. YOU. ARE. WELCOME.
